   116→## Configuration
   118→Tock supports a flexible configuration system using YAML files and environment variables.
   119→
   120→**Priority Order:**
   121→
   122→1. Command-line flags
   123→2. Environment variables
   124→3. Configuration file (`~/.config/tock/tock.yaml` or `./tock.yaml`)
   125→4. Default values
