   238→## Theming
   240→Tock supports customizable color themes for the calendar view.
   241→
   242→You can configure the theme in `tock.yaml`:
   243→
   244→```yaml
   245→theme:
   246→  name: custom
   247→  primary: "#ff0000"
   248→```
   249→
   250→Or use environment variables:
   251→
   252→### Theme Name
   262→### Auto-detection
   270→### Custom Colors
   283→### Example: Cyberpunk / Fuchsia Theme
